summary: This is an external email regarding grand jury time being reserved for the superseding indictment of Ghislaine Maxwell. It appears to be a communication between US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York and the FBI, with an attachment from NYPD.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: The subject of the email indicates grand jury time is being reserved for her superseding indictment.

events.title: Grand Jury Time Reserved for Maxwell Superseder
events.description: An email indicates grand jury time has been reserved for the superseding indictment of Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: Grand jury time was being reserved for a superseding indictment against Ghislaine Maxwell as of March 5, 2021.
The communication was between the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York and the FBI.
An attachment from the NYPD was included with the email.
